<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title><%= full_title(yield(:title)) %></title>

  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", media: "all", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Sarina|Poiret+One|PT+Serif|Open+Sans:400,300' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

  <!-- HTML5 shim, for IE6-8 support of HTML5 elements -->
  <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>
  <![endif]-->

</head>
<body>


<div class="container">

  <div class="masthead clearfix">
    <%= render 'layouts/header' %>
  </div>

  <hr>
  
  <div class="row main-content">

    <div class="offset1 span6 zone-content">
  
      <% flash.each do |key, value| %>
        <%= content_tag(:div, value, class: "alert alert-#{key}") %>
      <% end %>

      <%= yield %>

    </div>

    <aside id="aside-right" class="aside-column offset1 span3">
      <article class="widget-search-form widget">
        <header>
          <h1>Search</h1>
          </header>
        <form action="#" class="search-form" method="get">    
          <fieldset>
            <input id="q" name="q" type="text" value="">
            <!-- <button type="submit" class="button-icon"><i class="glyphicons-icon search white"></i></button> -->
            <button type="submit">Go</button>
          </fieldset>
        </form>
      </article>

      <article class="widget-tag-cloud widget">
        <header>
            <h1>Tag Cloud</h1>
        </header>
        <ul class="tagcloud">
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-1">
              <a href="#">Tag1</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-5">
              <a href="#">Tag2</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-3">
              <a href="#">Tag3</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-4">
              <a href="#">Tag4</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-2">
              <a href="#">Tag5</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-1">
              <a href="#">Tag6</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-2">
              <a href="#">Tag7</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-1">
              <a href="#">Tag8</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-5">
              <a href="#">Tag9</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-3">
              <a href="#">Tag10</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-4">
              <a href="#">Tag11</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-4">
              <a href="#">Tag12</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tagCloud-tag tagCloud-2">
              <a href="#">Tag13</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      
      <article class="widget-triple-first widget-html-widget widget">
        <header>
          <h1>Random</h1>
        </header>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Curabitur a nibh ut tortor dapibus vestibulum. Aliquam vel sem nibh. Suspendisse vel condimentum tellus.</p>
      </article>
    </aside>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <div class="row triple-row">
    <div id="triple-first" class="span4 triple">
      <div class="zone zone-triple-first">
        <article class="widget-triple-first widget-html-widget widget">
          <header>
            <h1>We happy?</h1>
          </header>
          <p>Normally, both your asses would be dead as fucking fried chicken, but you happen to pull this shit while I'm in a transitional period so I don't wanna kill you, I wanna help you.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="triple-second" class="span4 triple">
      <div class="zone zone-triple-second">
        <article class="widget-triple-second widget-html-widget widget">
          <header>
            <h1>Mmmm this is a tasty burger!</h1>
          </header>
          <p>Some pilots get picked and become television programs. Some don't, become nothing. She starred in one of the ones that became nothing.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="triple-third" class="span4 triple">
      <div class="zone zone-triple-third">
        <article class="widget-triple-third widget-html-widget widget">
          <header>
            <h1>Share &amp; Connect</h1>
          </header>
          <p>
            <a href="#"><i class="smicon-rss"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class="smicon-twitter"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class="smicon-google"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class="smicon-github"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class="smicon-reddit"></i></a>
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <hr>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="copyright span12">Copyuptight 2013. Umm because this space looked lost without something</div>  
  </div>

</div>  <!-- End Container -->
    
<%= debug(params) if Rails.env.development? %>
</body>
</html>
